eva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Ch&amp;iacute;nh thức hoặc b&amp;aacute;n thời gian.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong style=&quot;font-family: tahoma, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Mức lương:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: tahoma, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Thỏa thuận.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: tahoma, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Y&amp;ecirc;u cầu c&amp;ocirc;ng việc:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: tahoma, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Th&amp;agrave;nh thạo thao t&amp;aacute;c tr&amp;ecirc;n Photoshop.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: tahoma, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;- &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Kiến thức cơ bản về HTML, JavaScript, c&amp;oacute; khả năng ứng dụng c&amp;aacute;c thư viện hiệu ứng JQUERY.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: tahoma, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; C&amp;oacute; khiếu thẩm mỹ tốt, c&amp;oacute; t&amp;iacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ng tạo.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: tahoma, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Chịu được &amp;aacute;p lực c&amp;ocirc;ng việc, lu&amp;ocirc;n ho&amp;agrave;n th&amp;agrave;nh c&amp;ocirc;ng việc đ&amp;uacute;ng thời hạn.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: tahoma, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Nhiệt t&amp;igrave;nh trong c&amp;ocirc;ng việc.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: tahoma, geneva, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Ham học hỏi, y&amp;ecirc;u nghề.&lt